title: Shuihu Yingxiong Liezhuan
synopsis: The book "Water Margin" is based on the story of the Songjiang Uprising in the late Northern Song Dynasty. As we all know, the artistic achievement of "Water Margin" is most prominently manifested in the creation of heroes. The huge historical theme of the book is mainly expressed through the praise of the heroes of the uprising and the depiction of their struggle. Therefore, the success of the heroic image is an important factor for the brilliant artistic life of the work. In "Water Margin", at least ten or twenty typical images with distinctive personalities appear. These images are flesh and blood, lifelike, and vivid on paper. One hundred singles and eight generals refers to the 108 leaders on Liangshanpo in the novel "Water Margin", composed of 36 members of Tiangangxing and 72 members of Dishaxing. These 108 images are distinctive, flesh-and-blood, lifelike, and vivid on paper. They have their own strengths and have different endings. They are classic figures in the history of Chinese literature. "Water Margin·Heroes Biographies" is basically based on the original novel of "Water Margin", adopting a brand-new form-the biographical genre of Chinese Biography and History Books, to hide the deeds of every hero. Different from the film and television works reproduced in the previous official original works, "Water Margin·Heroes" adopts a new modern perspective, using modern thinking to deconstruct the character and the development and evolution of events, focusing on and highlighting each hero. The shining point of humanity that is worth our thinking. (translated from tenceng)

By chance, the horns on Luluqi's head gave off a peculiar light, releasing the double-sided being locked in a book. The devil, and the funny hero pigskin who fought with him. The entire animation story begins when Lu Luqi hunts down the Demon King in various regions of China, and the Demon King continues to calculate Lu Luqi’s conflicts and contradictions. (translated from youku)

title: Guoran Yi Ting
synopsis: "Sure enough, a town" uses an anthropomorphic approach to use the experience of a group of fruits in Binguo Town to show the growth and life of contemporary children. The characters are set with simple and honest big mouth, witty peach, beautiful flat, cute flatbread, lively jumping orange, naughty thin sweet and fat lotus, etc. They have quarrels and lies, tricks and pride, in Gradually grow with the help of the instructor and the understanding of the peers, and can accompany the small audience to make progress together. In the form of fairy tales, the humanities and affection of Changzhou are conveyed to children and parents through the image of fruits that children love very much. While subtly imparting knowledge, it also conveys deeper quality education content, which is conducive to improving children's ideological sentiment and nationality. Comprehensive qualities of culture and humanities (translated from douban)

title: Yuanlai Shi Zheyang
synopsis: Xiaowai and Chacha are good friends who love science. With the help of the doctor, they and their friends did a series of experiments to explore the mysteries of the universe. Of course, in the process of exploring the secrets, there are also various ridiculous episodes. I believe that in this cartoon, children can not only get entertainment, but also gain knowledge! (translated from tenceng)

title: Xiaoyao You Shijie
synopsis: Xiaoxiao, Yaoyao, Snoring Cat and Dada Dog are four good friends living on Xiaoyao Island. They study and play together in Xiaoyao School. Through the time and space shuttle device invented by Xiaoxiao, they traveled through ancient and modern China and foreign countries, and traveled around the world. Through the personal experiences of four small partners, they connected vivid and interesting stories. Using a modern perspective, they displayed ancient and modern wisdom and virtue stories in China and abroad. , Celebrity anecdotes, popular science knowledge, festivals around the world and the origin of various legends, deduct the wonderful "Travel around the world" (translated from iqiyi)

title: Tantei wa Mou, Shindeiru.
synopsis: Kimizuka Kimihiko is a crisis-magnet. From getting caught up in a crime scene to accidentally witnessing a drug deal, trouble seems to find him around every corner. So it is no surprise when his rather mundane flight suddenly enters a state of emergency with a dire need of a detective onboard. Unfortunately, his attempt at avoiding trouble is foiled by a beautiful girl with silver hair who goes by the codename Siesta. Declaring herself a detective, she unceremoniously drags Kimizuka into the case as her assistant. That incident spelled the beginning of an adventure around the globe that went beyond his wildest imagination. Putting their lives on the line, the two took down criminal organizations, prevented disasters, and saved thousands. But the curtain closed to their epic journey with Siesta's untimely death three years later. Resolving to live an ordinary high school life this time, Kimizuka spends a year maintaining a low profile. However, as fate would have it, a girl with an uncanny resemblance to Siesta comes crashing into his life, threatening to throw his peaceful days into disarray.

title: Gùshì zhěntou
synopsis: "Story Pillow" selects 52 Chinese idiom stories and folklore. Such as "Fox, Fake Tiger", "Remedy", "Cup Bow Snake Shadow", "Little Nian Beast", "Snail Girl", "Oil Weng", etc. A new interpretation and interpretation of classic stories is done in a way that children love to hear, and with novel and unique viewpoints. It aims to bring new ideas of early education with new ideas, develop children's imagination, stimulate children's logical thinking, inspire children's artistic creativity, and give children a way to express their own opinions. (translated from bilibili)

title: Budai Heshang Yun Youji Zhi Kanghong Fengyun
synopsis: During the period of the Five Dynasties, Mingzhou (now Ningbo, Zhejiang) came out of this monk from Changting Village in the north of Fenghua City, Mingzhou (now Ningbo, Zhejiang). He possessed stunts and was willing to do good things. One year, Budai monk wandered around Fenghua, and it happened to be flooded there. At this time, there was news that the court's disaster relief silver was robbed. During the period, Budai monk got acquainted with all kinds of partners, such as the scholar who loves to fight and hug, the eccentric little orphan, and the self-sacrificing beggar. In order to save the victims in dire straits, Budai monk, with the assistance of scholars, young orphans, and others, revealed the truth behind the looting of the disaster, brought corrupt officials and profiteers to justice, and helped the victims fight the flood and save themselves. (translated from iqiyi)

title: Jiāngziyá zhī shàng hú chuánshuō
synopsis: The Legend of Jiang Ziya’s Lake is a large-scale original cartoon on mythological theme produced by Paradise Cartoon 2010. It has 52 episodes. It mainly tells the legend of Jiang Shang, a great historical figure in ancient China. After extraordinary experience, he moved toward great virtue and wisdom, and finally became the story of a great sage of the ages. Jiang Shang has made great achievements in the fields of politics, military and economics. He is a cultural master of an era. Not only with his literary and martial arts. , With his noble personality and unremitting spirit of struggle, he has deeply influenced China's history and culture for thousands of years. Among the people, Jiang Shang has become a great virtue, great wisdom, supernatural power, "no taboo", and blessing the world. God. (translated from iqiyi)

title: Lunyu
synopsis: Use the form of animation to vividly teach Chinese traditional culture to children and increase their interest in such traditional masterpieces. (translated from tenceng)

title: Zeng Guang Xian Wen
synopsis: On the premise of maintaining the style of Chinese classical costumes, the enlightenment series of Guoxue has re-modernized the character image, which is more in line with the aesthetics of modern children, cute and delicate. At the same time, according to the psychological and intellectual characteristics of school-age children, the annotations and story text have been re-arranged and re-interpreted in simple and easy-to-understand language to make it easier for the baby to understand and find fun in it. (translated from tenceng)

title: Jisu Shaonian
synopsis: The story is that Lei Shou, the son of the mad emperor, could not understand what he did and left the mad emperor to go to No. 33 Middle School. Lei Shou met Han Bing, Yan Shi, and Situ Hongling in No. 33 Middle School. Together, they formed the No. 33 Middle School shuttle team to participate in the competition, and then Li Yanzhi from Diyuan Middle School also joined. Several teenagers struggled hard on the arena and finally reached the finals, but an accident occurred in the black finals. In order to save Holland, the whereabouts of the captain Lei Shou was unknown, the teenagers went their separate ways. One year later, Yan Shi returned and Han Bing received a special invitation letter from Henry, and everyone reorganized the team and renamed the Lightning Thunder Team to participate in world-class competitions.(translated from iqiyi)

title: Xuanfeng Sudu
synopsis: The story of a group of enthusiastic teenagers participating in the national remote control car competition. Through rounds of fierce competitions, the angel team formed by Ajian from Xicheng Middle School and the Tianma team formed by Kajie from Dongcheng Academy met in the semifinals. Ajian lost to Kajie in the competition due to lack of experience, and the result of the match caused him to be hit hard. With the encouragement of Coach Li, A Jian revived and participated in the new national competition. After learning from the experience of past competitions, he finally defeated Kajie of the Demon Team in the game and won the national competition. (translated from tenceng)

title: Xiong Xiaomi He Ta De Hao Pengyou
synopsis: Excellent work that won the Best Animation Television Film Award. Xiong Xiaomi is a smart, gentle, optimistic, healthy and cheerful little bear. He is helpful and willing to make friends. He is a good boy who can easily get the recognition of others. It mainly tells all kinds of interesting stories about Xiong Xiaomi's interactions with his friends. (translated from iqiyi)

title: Xiao Xiao Huajia Xiong Xiaomi
synopsis: The enthusiastic and smart Xiong Xiaomi and his friends Penguin Zhiping, Little Elephant Ellie, Moose Muz, Lion Lei, etc. have encountered various problems that need to be solved in their lives. Xiong Xiaomi and the others invited the magic paintbrush to draw Friends who can help them solve their problems. In the story, the friends drawn by Xiong Xiaomi have magically become alive, and they solved the problem together. In the interesting story, the children met various animals, Vehicles, plants, and also learned how to paint them. I hope that through these stories, children can fall in love with painting, fall in love with painting, and express their emotions bravely with painting. (translated from iqiyi)

title: Zhihui Zidan Che
synopsis: Transfer student Yun Feng came to the new campus and was hit by a cool toy car falling from the sky. Because of this "accident", Yun Feng got to know the bullet car player and neighbor Yan Hui, and then let him do it. A smart bullet car that excites and fights for. Through the growth of Yunfeng, this film shows the children's friendship and perseverance, and shows the unique youthful vitality of young people. (translated from iqiyi)

title: Si Du Chishui
synopsis: The film uses animated documentary techniques to reproduce historical events such as the Battle of the Xiangjiang River, the Zunyi Conference, the Crossing of Chishui River, and the crossing of the Jinsha River. (translated from tenceng)

title: Yi Suo Yuyan
synopsis: "Aesop's Fables" embodies the truths in daily life that are not perceptible to us through short little fables. These short stories are concise and easy to approach. Not only does it have many readers, it also has a significant influence in the history of literature. ()translated from tenceng

title: Huanle Zhi Cheng
synopsis: In the ancient horizon, there is a beautiful city of joy, where people have been living a peaceful and happy life under the protection of the book of joy. However, there are always shadows on the back of the light. An abandoned black cat inadvertently hid into the tower on a stormy night to avoid the cold. He turned into a woman because he accidentally peeked at the Tome of Joy, and the excited black cat raised the Tome of Joy. Who knew that as soon as the Tome was opened, something terrible happened: the dragon suppressed by the Tome rose into the sky. Lightning and thunder, the originally beautiful and peaceful city of joy fell into ruins and split into several pieces in an instant, all the residents were turned into various objects, and the treasures disappeared. With the help of the mysterious man, Happy Baby found the Shenlong Cave on the island. But Huanhuan and Lele were injured by Shenlong, and Doudou was swallowed by Shenlong. Huanhuan and Lele were rescued by the mysterious man. Under the guidance of the mysterious man, Huanhuan upgraded his equipment and Lele learned the fire technology. They fought the Shenlong again, and the Shenlong spit out the peas and returned the treasure. The treasure did not generate magical power, and the happy babies embarked on a new journey. (translated from iqiyi)

synopsis: A hot fighting game played at the girls' school!! Aya transferred into Kuromi Girls Academy a month ago with the goal of changing herself into a proper lady. After meeting the breathtaking Shirayuri, Aya is blown away by her elegance and posterity. Imagine her surprise when she finds Shirayuri after school playing... a fighting game?! And if that wasn't perplexing enough, she is challenged to a duel by the unladylike Shirayuri!  (Source: MU)

title: Santa Company: Manatsu no Merry Christmas
synopsis: Santa Company is an original work brought to life by Kenji Itoso. A short animation was released in 2014 after a successful crowdfunding campaign, followed by a feature-length version released in Japan in 2019. This work is a spin-off featuring some of the same characters. Upon their visit to a tropical island just below the equator, Mint and co. from Santa Company find themselves confronted with a mountain of ocean debris. Small acts of carelessness upon carelessness have, quite literally, piled up into a big problem—just what have Mint and the others gotten themselves into...? A splendid, yet strange, secret Christmas story. (Source: Official Site)

title: Yun Qi Feixing Riji
synopsis: "Yunqi Flying Diary" is the world's first flying-themed 3D high-definition TV animation. It was created by Harbin Pinge Culture Communication Co., Ltd. in two years. There are 78 episodes and each episode lasts 10 minutes. The film uses fresh, cute cartoon images, relaxed, humorous and interesting stories, combines science and education with entertainment, and conveys aviation knowledge to children in happiness. Tuantuan Airport, located on the coast of a satellite city, is a magnificent international airport. One day, Yunqi from a small town joined the Tuantuan Airport. The huge scale of the Tuantuan Airport aroused Yunqi's keen interest in the complex and busy. The airport work is full of expectations. In the life of Tuantuan Airport for a period of time, the brave and righteous Yunqi tried to overcome difficulties. Through a series of earth-shaking events, he met many airplane friends with different personalities at the airport. Yunqi loves his work, and finally through his unremitting efforts, he accumulated a wealth of flying experience, and step by step toward his dream of traveling the world. (translated from tenceng)

title: Gelin Tonghua (2014)
synopsis: It is a classic of the world's fairy tales. Since its inception, it has had extensive influence all over the world. The Brothers Grimm told the children magical and romantic fairy tales with their rich imagination and beautiful language. (translated from tenceng)

title: Sanzijing(2014)
synopsis: "San Zi Jing" is a traditional Chinese enlightenment textbook. Among the ancient Chinese classics, "San Zi Jing" is one of the most obvious and easy to understand readers. The "Three Characters Classic" includes examples of traditional Chinese culture, including literature, history, philosophy, astronomy, geography, ethics and justice, loyalty and filial piety, etc. The core ideas include "benevolence, righteousness, honesty, respect, and filial piety." While reciting the "San Zi Jing", I learned about common sense, traditional Chinese studies and historical stories, as well as the principles of life and things in the story.(translated from tenceng)

title: Hong Hai Er Yu Daxueyuan
synopsis: Hong Haier is a good fortune boy next to Guanyin Bodhisattva. The red boy who practiced beside the Bodhisattva got rid of the devil. He was brave and witty, enthusiastic and optimistic, and had a sense of justice. One day, Guanyin Bodhisattva had a foreboding that the natural environment around the "Nine Heavens" giant tree would face a catastrophe, so he sent the red boy to a graduate school. At the graduate school, Honghaier was exposed to various courses in Chinese studies, arithmetic, and martial arts, and also met five partners. Each of these five friends has their own unique skills, and gradually became the right arm of the red boy. Honghaier and his five partners live a happy and lively college life every day. (translated from acfun)

title: Hong Hai Er Zhi Pa Pa Wa Xun Shi Ji
synopsis: Honghaier and his five partners, Ao Man, Zhuzhu, Jindou, Yindou, and Kaka, live a happy campus life. On the campus, the stone statue of the Five Elements God was destroyed. With the help of the sensing ability of the sacred beast and the frog, Hong Haier and his friends embarked on a journey to find the stone. Hong Haier is not afraid of hardships and dangers, and leads his partners to bravely face difficulties and defeat powerful enemies, and finally obtains the five-color god stone. (translated from iqiyi)
